data.oai_dc:dc: Foraging tray, seed removal and visitation data

Data collected in Stage 2 Scotia Wildlife Sanctuary, NSW, Australia. Foraging tray data including spoor recorded and number of seeds removed from tray from a possible 50. 5 treatments were applied within a block including mammal exclusion, ant exclusion, procedural control ant exclusion, procedural control mammal exclusion, control.
